â€¢ Use one mask per day
â€¢ Make sure the wire on top sits on your nose all the time and you can bend the metal at the top to fit your face

â€¢ If you are wearing the mask for long period of time you can place piece of tissue inside just infront of your mouth and you can replace that as you go
